data.description: Fusion of comfort and style in this 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhouse, highlighted by its spacious family room adorned with soaring ceilings, abundant natural light, and tranquil views extending to the open backyard space. Beautiful Kitchen with S.S. appliances, modern shaker cabinets, and quartz countertops with an amazing walk-in pantry perfect for storing all your items. The open-layout kitchen/dining room combo is perfect for entertaining. Upstairs, the main suite is a true sanctuary, complete with a large walk-in closet, sitting area, and a luxurious newly updated bathroom featuring a double vanity and stunning rainfall shower. Plenty of closets throughout and a convenient 2nd-floor laundry room. Beautifully finished basement with an extra storage area.
